(1) Phase Header View
  - fires when `phase.name` changes

(2) Flow Column Component
  - fires when `flow.title` changes
  - fires when `editing` changes


Paper Manage View
  - fires when `didInsertElement`
  - fires when a phase is added or removed
  (1) Phase Header View


MMT Edit View
  - fires when `didInsertElement`
  - fires when `controller.editMode`
  (1) Phase Header View


Flow Manager View
  - fires when `didInsertElement`
  - fires when flow is added or removed
  (2) Flow Column Component


Journal Flow Manager View
  - fires when `didInsertElement`
  - fires when flow is added or removed
  (2) Flow Column Component

Journal Flow Manager Controller
 - fires afterRender after a flow is saved
